<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="background: #f1f1f1">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <% include ../parent/static.ejs %>
    <title><%= com.env.seo.title %>帮助中心</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header" ><a class="iconfont" href="/help"><img src="/img/fh1.png" class="fh_img"></a>充值投资</div>

<div class="help_lists">
    <ul class="help_main">
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>我们如何充值？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2"  style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p> 四个步骤就可以充值成功： </p>
                    <p>①登录账户，进入【我的账户】，点击“充值”；</p>
                    <p> ②输入充值金额；</p>
                    <p> ③可以选择快捷充值或者网银充值；</p>
                    <p>④付款后，显示成功付款并跳转到铂恒金服页面，显示充值成功。</p>

                </div>
            </div>

        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg"  class="img1">
                <span>充值支持哪些银行？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png"  class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2"  style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>充值页面会提示您支持充值的银行。点击选择不同银行可查看对应银行的充值限额。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>铂恒金服支持哪些网银？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>为铂恒金服提供第三方支付上海富友，支持网银包括：工、农、中、建，各家股份制银行、地方商业银行在内的多家银行进行合作。具体信息请登录后，在【我的账户】页面中点击“充值” 查看。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>充值时会扣手续费吗？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>充值对投资人是免费的，充值手续费由铂恒金服平台承担</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>是否可以用信用卡充值？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>暂时不支持信用卡进行充值。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>投资如何进行投资？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>根据项目类型、项目周期、年化利率选择标的投资。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>银行支付限额</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p><img src="/img/yhx_2.png" width="100%"> </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
<% include ../parent/slide_nav.ejs %>
</body>
</html>